    "updated_at": "2016-09-01T08:29:24Z",
    "body": "@artiya4u You have to place the full path of the `index.html` file in the `loadURL('file:///full_path/index.html')`\n\nIf you get the errors I was getting in the screenshot above, make sure that when you initialise the `BrowserWindow` you do it with the `nodeIntegration` option set to false\n\n`new BrowserWindow({width: 1024, height: 764, title: \"yourApp\", webPreferences: {\"nodeIntegration\":false}});`\n"
